    Índice de funciones

    Development Regions

    Functions and datasets for working with development regions in the Dominican Republic.

    DR_REG
    Simple features for the "Development Regions of the Dominican Republic"
    dr_region
    Metadata for the "Development Regions of the Dominican Republic"

    Provinces

    Functions and datasets for handling provinces in the Dominican Republic.

    DR_PROV
    Simple features for the "Provinces of the Dominican Republic"
    dr_province
    Metadata for the "Provinces of the Dominican Republic"
    remesas_provincias
    Percentage distribution by provinces of remittances received by the Dominican Republic

    Municipalities

    Functions and datasets for dealing with municipalities in the Dominican Republic.

    DR_MUN
    Simple features for the "Municipalities of the Dominican Republic"
    dr_municipality
    Metadata for the "Municipalities of the Dominican Republic"

    Municipal Districts

    Functions and datasets for managing municipal districts in the Dominican Republic.

    DR_DM
    Simple features for the "Municipal Districts of the Dominican Republic"
    dr_municipal_district
    Metadata for the "Municipal Districts of the Dominican Republic"

    Sections

    Functions and datasets for working with sections in the Dominican Republic.

    DR_SEC
    Simple features for the "Sections of the Dominican Republic"
    dr_section
    Metadata for the "Sections of the Dominican Republic"
